WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.101 --> 00:00:04.428
Here are the formatted subtitles:

00:00:04.428 --> 00:00:04.640
---

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:09.520
The most revolutionary breakthrough
of this age is the collective

00:00:09.520 --> 00:00:12.480
inner transformation
of the human being.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:15.280
This is the next stage
in our evolution.

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:18.800
The forth to mention that will
awaken us to become

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:22.640
highly evolved human beings
with the ability,

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:26.560
to have no more personality,
that can save ourselves

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:27.920
and save our world…

00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:33.600
It is an honour to present
Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:36.960
world spiritual leader and founder
of Sahaja Yoga.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:40.560
Please join us a reel women
for the forth to mention

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:50.960
of evolution.

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:29.520
It is time now in our evolution
to introspect deeply

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.920
into the problems of
modern human being

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:35.200
and to find an answer
and a solution

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.360
for inner and global peace…

00:01:37.360 --> 00:01:40.800
If we are to avoid
our own self-destruction,

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:44.640
in a cleric world then we must
limit the Science,

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:48.800
rationality, religion, power
and money has left us wanting

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:51.440
all of us…
Rich, Poor, Black and White…

00:01:51.440 --> 00:01:55.040
And we have looked for truth
in all the wrong places

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:57.680
But these are special times…
The Blossom Times!

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:00.720
That has been prophesied
in all the ancient texts.

00:02:00.720 --> 00:02:04.160
It is the last judgement,
the age of Aquarius

00:02:04.160 --> 00:02:08.560
and is the profound opportunity
to enter the fourth dimension

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:12.000
Where we can become highly evolved
spiritual beings

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:15.040
and to know on our
central nervous system

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.920
And we can prove God
like a science.

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:24.640
It is a deep honour to present
Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:26.240
who is the world spiritual leader,

00:02:26.240 --> 00:02:30.640
Who has travelled all over the world
to give en-mass self-realisation

00:02:30.640 --> 00:02:31.920
to thousands.

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:35.600
She is here to talk about
the new and long-awaited book…

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:39.840
Meta Modern Era…
Welcome, Shri Mataji!

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.560
It is so wonderful to have you!

00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:45.600
It is hard to pronounce
Meta Modern era.

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:46.960
What does it mean?

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:52.240
Meta Modern Era…
The modern era is the present times.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:54.320
And meta is beyond that.

00:02:54.320 --> 00:02:56.720
What is beyond that?

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:58.480
To go beyond the mind!

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:01.920
No, No not mind.
Beyond this time.

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:05.920
What is beyond this time
We expect…

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:08.640
What is the goal of writing
the book?

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:12.160
What is it you want to achieve?
And What did you want to say?

00:03:12.880 --> 00:03:19.200
I wanted to tell them,
about the power you all have…

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:23.840
All of you…
Whether you belong to one religion

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:25.200
or to another.

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:29.600
Whether you are White, Yellow,
Red, anything you may be…

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:33.600
It's not skin deep.
It is very deep within us

00:03:33.600 --> 00:03:36.400
in the triangular bone
called as Sacrum.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:39.760
That shows that even the Greeks
knew that it is a sacrum bone…

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:40.640
There is a power you all have…

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:45.600
All of you have the power
which if it is awakened,

00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:49.680
you achieve the fourth dimension
of your personality.

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:53.280
But the problem that exists today
in this world

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:58.000
is because our heritage comes
from the Animal Kingdom.

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:01.360
And we have many things
which belong to the animals.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:07.440
The worst thing is that we have
also thinking power and rationality

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:10.240
so we justify even
whatever we do wrong.

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:13.280
So even it is worse than
animal stage sometimes…

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:16.160
Yes, you call Rationality
the curse of modern man.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:20.160
Of course, Rationality
can explain everything.

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:23.440
You may do any wrong and it
explains that it is all right…

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:25.429
I mean that's how it is.
It is very dangerous.

00:04:25.429 --> 00:04:30.880
The people like Floyd,
they made rational everything.

00:04:30.880 --> 00:04:36.000
Like then it is emotional,
the human being is going to be

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:41.600
a spiritual being and that happens
when this power within you rises…

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:44.720
through six centres,
pierces through your fontanel

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:50.240
bone area and connects to your
all-pervading power of divine love.

00:04:50.240 --> 00:04:53.440
Now that is called as 'Ruh'
by some people…

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:56.880
In the Bible, it is written as
'Cool Breeze of the Holy Ghost'

00:04:56.880 --> 00:05:00.880
and in other scriptures also
it is described very clearly

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:04.720
especially in Indian Scriptures
as 'Param Chaitanya'.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.840
But the trouble with human beings
is that they are capable

00:05:07.840 --> 00:05:09.520
of spoiling anything.

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:13.600
If they go to a forest,
it will be all clean, nicely,

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.520
preserved sort of a thing.

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:19.200
But once a human being enters there
you start spoiling it…

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:25.120
You say that even in America
we have 200 years of history

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:28.400
and in such a short time
we have made such a massive hit.

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:36.320
You call it a Coca-Cola culture.
Why did you call that, Mother?

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:40.240
You see the culture is more
money-oriented…

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:42.960
Somehow you should get money…

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:46.240
I mean it goes to such an extent
that people think killing is alright

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:48.560
for money, doing anything
is alright for money…

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:53.040
Money has its own purpose
but it is not for the destruction…

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:55.280
It is for the construction
of human being

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:58.000
and it's not so important also…

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:01.120
See it is the thing that
we don't have the satisfaction…

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:04.080
Today we want to buy a car,
alright,

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:07.920
for that we will work hard,
save money, buy one car.

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:10.720
But after buying it
there is no satisfaction,

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:12.640
then you want to build a house!

00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:17.040
Then you go from one to another,
never ever enjoying

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:17.920
what you have achieved…

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:21.760
Isn't that Slavery, Mother?
Slavery to advertising…

00:06:21.760 --> 00:06:25.440
No, No, due to greed…
Greed in human being.

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:33.120
And this Greed comes to us
from ancient things like Inheritance…

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:38.320
But they are satisfied…
Animals are satisfied at a point

00:06:38.320 --> 00:06:39.360
but we are not.

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:42.800
We are very Greedy,
and we start running after this greed

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:45.120
that has no end.

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:49.200
This also makes us
a little bit competitive

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:51.040
and all kinds of things come in…

00:06:51.040 --> 00:06:54.000
And all kinds of cruelties
come in too.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:57.560
Rich people think they are
superior to others,

00:06:57.560 --> 00:06:58.880
but it's not so.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:01.200
Because it has not given
them satisfaction…

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:03.760
Whatever they have,
they are not satisfied.

00:07:03.760 --> 00:07:08.400
That's the first thing that shows
that they are not very much higher

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:10.880
in their awareness…

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:14.160
With this happening,
it passes through the six centres.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:18.160
Now, these six centres are
responsible for our physical,

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:22.320
mental, emotional and spiritual
being all of them…

00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:27.280
So when she rises,
this power which is the Kundalini,

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:29.280
which is your individual Mother,

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:32.960
She knows everything about you,
She knows your past,

00:07:32.960 --> 00:07:36.800
She knows your hankering,
She knows your aspirations,

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:37.760
everything…

00:07:37.760 --> 00:07:39.680
She has tape-recorded it,

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:44.400
and when She awakens and rises
above the six centres…

00:07:44.400 --> 00:07:47.200
What happens is that
the centres get enlightened…

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:48.880
Then they get integrated…

00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:51.760
And when it pierces through
the fontanel bone area

00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:54.800
it becomes one with this
all-pervading power…

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:57.360
Now we have all these beautiful
flowers here

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.960
but we just take them
for granted.

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:02.640
We just don't understand
how different flowers are grown

00:08:02.640 --> 00:08:06.880
differently in a different manner
from the same soil…

00:08:06.880 --> 00:08:09.680
How does our mother earth
do all this miracle?

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:15.840
Or we see our heart running
and we ask a doctor…

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:17.680
Who is running our heart…

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:19.920
He will say it is an
autonomous nervous system…

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:22.800
But if you ask who is this auto…
they can't answer…

00:08:24.320 --> 00:08:27.680
There is a scientific culture…
We need proof of everything.

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:29.200
That's all right!
You can prove it.

00:08:29.200 --> 00:08:30.160
We can prove it?

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:32.880
Yes, We can prove everything.
Whatever I am saying…

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:34.080
Can be proved.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:37.440
But you must turn your eyes
to the truth also…

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:39.680
To find out what is the truth
really…

00:08:39.680 --> 00:08:42.640
In a sincere manner
you can find out…

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:46.320
For example, the scientist himself
said that there is a Torsion area

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:49.760
beyond our mind,
means beyond rationality.

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:51.360
There is a torsion area.

00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:54.000
And if you can reach
that torsion area

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:57.840
you can get the truth before you,

00:08:57.840 --> 00:09:00.560
and that can be verified
by science.

00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:05.840
He himself was so tired
finding out the theory of relativity.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:10.160
In the laboratory he was searching
and was so tired,

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:14.800
so he went into the garden
and was playing with soap bubbles…

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:19.600
And there he says suddenly
from somewhere unknown

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.360
this theory dawned upon me…

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:24.400
It happens to all the scientists
but they don't know the area.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:28.800
He has precisely called it
as the Torsion area.

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:30.800
Didn't it happen to you too,
Mother?

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:34.320
Didn't it happen to you
by a tree in your meditation,

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.640
like you discovered
en-mass realisation?

00:09:36.640 --> 00:09:38.800
I was born like this…
I should say.

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:41.440
So nothing happened that way.

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:44.480
But I was more anxious
about one thing.

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:46.640
That I said this state
must be reached…

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:50.160
This stage of self-knowledge
and self-realisation

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:51.760
by everyone in this world…

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:54.800
That was my research,
or I should say

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:57.440
that was my greatest desire,

00:09:57.440 --> 00:10:00.320
so I tried to study
human beings in a subtle way…

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:02.080
What's the problem with them?

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:05.760
Because formerly only one person
could get self-realisation

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.840
among thousands of them,

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:12.480
and that was the tradition —
to give it to one person only…

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:14.480
So then I thought
why not everyone,

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:17.280
because unless and until
everyone gets it,

00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:20.320
it's not going to work out well
for the one who gets it,

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:24.160
because you have seen all saints
have been tortured, troubled,

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:27.040
crucified,
because others did not know

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:27.760
what it was.

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:29.920
So they thought
he is talking something rubbish.

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:31.600
Whatever it is…

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:34.320
So it has to happen
to the collective.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:37.120
Thus I tried to find out
about human beings.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.680
Luckily my father was
a very social person,

00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:41.280
my husband also.

00:10:41.280 --> 00:10:45.200
As a result, I found out in 1970
the method by which

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:48.080
you can give a mass-realisation.

00:10:49.440 --> 00:10:53.840
And for that mass realisation
I started working with one lady,

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:56.800
to begin with…
Gradually it started growing.

00:10:56.800 --> 00:11:00.080
Now they tell me
72 nations are following…

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:04.960
Are you surprised at how many
people are practising Sahaja Yoga?

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:08.320
Did you expect this?

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:10.640
Only I thought that
if it works, it will work!

00:11:10.640 --> 00:11:12.640
But I expect more to come now.

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:15.280
What is this very special
time period?

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:19.840
Is it called Krita Yuga?
What does that mean?

00:11:19.840 --> 00:11:22.560
The cycle of Krita Yuga?

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.945
Yes, a very special time period.
That is why I called it Krita Yuga.

00:11:24.945 --> 00:11:28.560
See, the first was 'Kalyuga',
which was the worst of all…

00:11:29.280 --> 00:11:31.600
They are described
in the Shastras also.

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:36.480
But they didn't go that far.
They didn't visit America to see.

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:47.520
At the most, they said
that the children will answer back

00:11:47.520 --> 00:11:49.920
their parents and all that
was written…

00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:52.000
But if you come to America
you will realize

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:59.600
it's a completely very dangerous
picture of the 'Kalyuga'…

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:02.080
After 'Kalyuga', comes 'Krita Yuga'

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:05.200
where this all-pervading power
starts working out…

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:06.720
through human beings…

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:08.560
That's started in the beginning,

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:11.760
and then after that
will come 'Satyuga'.

00:12:11.760 --> 00:12:13.680
I think the Satyuga
has also started…

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:16.240
Where everything
will be exposed…

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:17.520
Falsehood, everything…

00:12:17.520 --> 00:12:18.020
Yes.

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:25.520
Shri Mataji, people in America
are crazy for this Y2K…

00:12:25.520 --> 00:12:28.320
They think this is
the end of the world.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:31.360
They think that once 2000 comes
all the computers will start erasing.

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:33.840
We are going to have the end…

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:40.480
And people are preparing,
building walls

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:43.680
and arming themselves for war…
This is going on…

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:46.320
What do you say about that?

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:48.720
No, No…
You see our creator who has created

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:52.640
us is not going to allow
this destruction.

00:12:52.640 --> 00:12:54.720
Of course, this is
the last judgement,

00:12:54.720 --> 00:13:00.000
so those who do not rise above
their human awareness

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:01.280
might be lost,

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:05.360
but not people who are achieving
their greater awareness…

00:13:05.360 --> 00:13:06.560
They won't be lost.

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:11.520
And our creator himself
has placed this great power within us

00:13:11.520 --> 00:13:14.240
to have our ascent into
this fourth dimension.

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:18.000
So world peace is possible, Mother?

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.800
Of course, I mean,
when this happens to you,

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:23.040
you become extremely peaceful…

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:28.720
Now look at our thoughts!
They come from the future sometimes,

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:31.520
from the past,
and we dance in the cusp

00:13:31.520 --> 00:13:32.560
of those thoughts.

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:35.680
All the time we are dancing.
We cannot stop thinking.

00:13:35.680 --> 00:13:39.440
But when this power rises,
She elongates them

00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:41.600
and there is a space in between —

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:47.040
that is the space of the present
where you are silent…

00:13:47.040 --> 00:13:50.400
You watch everything,
you react to nothing,

00:13:50.400 --> 00:13:53.600
you just absorb, absorb it…

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:57.200
For example —
I see a beautiful carpet here,

00:13:57.200 --> 00:13:59.840
so I look at it,
how beautiful it is!

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:04.000
I am having all the enjoyment
of the artist who created it…

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:08.640
But I don't go on thinking —
how much did you pay?

00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:13.120
Where can I get it?
Or if it is mine, should we insure it?

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:15.360
All these nonsensical ideas
don't come…

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:19.920
The beauty you just start watching,
and watching the beauty

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:23.440
is a source of great joy to you.

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:28.960
So if you see a human being
who is so reactionary to everything,

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:32.560
they go mad…

00:14:32.560 --> 00:14:33.920
So you have to be silent…

00:14:33.920 --> 00:14:36.960
And when you are silent,
you are peaceful…

00:14:36.960 --> 00:14:39.360
Unless and until there is peace
within yourself,

00:14:39.360 --> 00:14:43.440
you can't create peace by bombs…
Can you?

00:14:45.440 --> 00:14:49.600
So you want to transform people
and political power?

00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:50.800
That's the hope?

00:14:52.160 --> 00:14:55.760
That is our destiny!
Every human being has the right

00:14:55.760 --> 00:14:57.040
to get it…

00:14:57.040 --> 00:15:00.160
Sahaja — 'Saha' means 'with',
'ja' is 'born'.

00:15:00.160 --> 00:15:04.240
Shri Mataji, when I met with yogis,
I was very impressed —

00:15:04.240 --> 00:15:07.440
they have a look in their eyes…
I wanted to be like them…

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:20.463
I wanted to love like them,
and that is the true meaning

00:15:20.463 --> 00:15:20.480
of Sahaja Yoga…

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:25.760
Yes, their eyes are glittering
and they don't fight,

00:15:25.760 --> 00:15:29.911
they love each other,
and it is not an artificial thing…

00:15:29.911 --> 00:15:32.640
They are just natural,
and even if they are from

00:15:32.640 --> 00:15:36.080
different countries,
I have seen them so nicely blended,

00:15:37.040 --> 00:15:40.400
enjoying each other,
loving each other…

00:15:40.400 --> 00:15:44.080
They find they have found
their brothers all over…

00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:46.480
sisters all over…

00:15:46.480 --> 00:15:50.400
Sahaja Yoga has had many
American Breakthroughs.

00:15:50.400 --> 00:15:52.640
Can you tell us about them, Mother?
especially in America,

00:15:52.640 --> 00:15:55.520
they love to know
that it can cure cancer…

00:15:55.520 --> 00:15:57.680
I have already had a hospital
in India,

00:15:57.680 --> 00:15:59.600
and another one
we are going to have…

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:02.400
This is near Bombay…
Another one we are going to have

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:03.520
is in Delhi…

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:07.760
Where we treat them freely
because it is their own power.

00:16:07.760 --> 00:16:10.800
So we can't charge them,
but for their stay and food,

00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:12.400
of course, we charge them…

00:16:12.400 --> 00:16:15.520
It's a very remarkable thing
which we have found out.

00:16:15.520 --> 00:16:18.080
That most of the diseases
can be cured

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:20.000
by the awakening of the Kundalini,

00:16:20.000 --> 00:16:22.880
because diseases come to you
because of the imbalance

00:16:22.880 --> 00:16:24.400
of your centres…

00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:26.400
With the exhaustion of the centres.

00:16:26.400 --> 00:16:28.640
But this Kundalini,
when She rises,

00:16:28.640 --> 00:16:30.640
She nourishes them,
and not only that,

00:16:30.640 --> 00:16:32.000
She integrates them.

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:34.400
Cancer has been cured
in many people…

00:16:34.400 --> 00:16:36.560
Has it been documented
by Scientific Research?

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:38.000
Of course, of course,
we have doctors,

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:40.000
they have documented…

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:44.600
Wow! Even Genes can be changed…
How many souls can be changed?

00:16:44.600 --> 00:16:46.480
Yes, in my book
I have written about this.

00:16:47.280 --> 00:16:49.520
And I have also written
about Phosphorous…

00:16:49.520 --> 00:16:52.800
When there is too much phosphorous
in the body, in the genes,

00:16:52.800 --> 00:16:55.040
because of dry temperament,
you see…

00:16:56.400 --> 00:17:00.080
So a person becomes
very hot-tempered.

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:05.520
Can also get what you would call
a person who is easily irritated,

00:17:05.520 --> 00:17:08.880
very overactive sort of a person…

00:17:08.880 --> 00:17:14.000
But in case you get your realisation
you get so balanced…

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:18.640
Will you speak about women, Mother?

00:17:20.560 --> 00:17:26.120
In the book you talk about why,
if it's so natural and so normal,

00:17:26.120 --> 00:17:29.440
then why do we so violently
go against it?

00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:42.480
And why do our value systems
not hold up?

00:17:42.480 --> 00:17:45.440
See, I don't know
how they don't understand

00:17:45.440 --> 00:17:49.840
that these things create
horrible diseases…

00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:53.840
They are creating horrible diseases,
scientifically proved,

00:17:53.840 --> 00:17:56.560
but still they indulge in it
because they think they have

00:17:56.560 --> 00:17:57.840
the freedom to ruin their lives.

00:17:57.840 --> 00:18:02.480
What can we do about it?
This kind of attitude they take.

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:05.600
And they are going on,
and I just don't know

00:18:05.600 --> 00:18:08.400
how to tell them
that this is all wrong.

00:18:08.400 --> 00:18:11.200
While you try to be moral,
which is one of the centres

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:18.160
which is below this Kundalini
and is the centre for morality,

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:20.800
that has to be alright.

00:18:20.800 --> 00:18:26.000
And that's the one
which makes you stabilise yourself…

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:30.480
Now I have seen that some people
we didn't allow to be there…

00:18:30.480 --> 00:18:34.880
Because I have great sympathy
for them

00:18:34.880 --> 00:18:37.600
and I wanted to start
even a hospital for that…

00:18:37.600 --> 00:18:41.760
But they are so arrogant,
they know they are going to die,

00:18:41.760 --> 00:18:43.760
so they think they can do
whatever they want…

00:18:43.760 --> 00:18:50.000
They shout, scream…
And they form a group to attack us…

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:52.960
It's impossible to make
them understand that you are sick,

00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:56.880
you can be saved
if you try to follow Sahaja Yoga,

00:18:56.880 --> 00:18:59.600
but they are very difficult…
Rather, the most difficult patients

00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:00.560
I have seen…

00:19:00.560 --> 00:19:02.560
Otherwise, other patients
are all right,

00:19:02.560 --> 00:19:08.080
and so many diseases —
cancer and other muscular diseases —

00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:11.120
so many other kinds of diseases
have already been cured

00:19:11.120 --> 00:19:12.560
by Sahaja Yoga.

00:19:12.560 --> 00:19:14.800
So first they used to come
and tell Sahaja Yogis,

00:19:14.800 --> 00:19:16.800
so I thought better to have
hospitals!

00:19:16.800 --> 00:19:20.160
So now we have a hospital
in Bombay, near Bombay,

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:23.120
there are 175 patients already…

00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:26.560
And another one
we are starting here in Delhi.

00:19:26.560 --> 00:19:30.480
Wonderful! Also Mother,
how can we stop

00:19:30.480 --> 00:19:38.800
the inhumanity to a woman?
How can we stop this?

00:19:38.800 --> 00:19:41.160
Men are inhuman to a woman,
and sometimes

00:19:41.160 --> 00:19:46.720
the woman is inhuman to men.
It's quite a lot here, right?

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:49.120
You really take a stand,
Mother…

00:19:49.120 --> 00:19:52.560
You say media is the absolute
reason for it…

00:19:52.560 --> 00:19:55.440
For the value system going down…

00:19:55.440 --> 00:19:59.200
I am not interested in this media
because they don't understand

00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:01.120
how irresponsible they are!

00:20:01.120 --> 00:20:03.760
All that goes wrong
could be blamed on them…

00:20:03.760 --> 00:20:07.040
They don't understand
that it is a very important thing

00:20:07.040 --> 00:20:09.680
for media to be responsible

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:12.320
and to understand
what they are up to.

00:20:12.320 --> 00:20:16.960
Because money-making is the aim…
If that is the only thing

00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:19.200
to be achieved…
What can you talk to them?

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:22.240
But they should understand
that they are very responsible,

00:20:22.240 --> 00:20:25.680
heavily responsible
for all the destruction

00:20:25.680 --> 00:20:26.960
that has taken place…

00:20:28.400 --> 00:20:30.080
Another term —
the Law of Polarity —

00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:34.080
you talked about in the book.
The Law of Polarity meaning?

00:20:34.080 --> 00:20:35.760
Yes, it reacts…

00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:39.600
If you go to one extreme
it reacts in the other extreme…

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:42.480
So one should not go to extremes,
in anything,

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:44.880
you should be in the centre…

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:49.760
And in many countries right now
they are suffering

00:20:49.760 --> 00:20:51.040
from the law of polarity?

00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:55.520
Yes, Yes, any country…
You see when it goes too much

00:20:55.520 --> 00:20:57.200
to the extremes…

00:20:57.200 --> 00:21:01.680
Now I would say in America —
you are alright, prosperous,

00:21:01.680 --> 00:21:03.840
everything,
but I find everybody indebted…

00:21:06.800 --> 00:21:11.600
I am amazed that in India also
many people, well educated,

00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:14.400
are indebted.
They have debts on them.

00:21:14.400 --> 00:21:18.320
So I said, why, why should
you be indebted?

00:21:18.320 --> 00:21:23.920
This is the lifestyle — such that
they have to carry on the lifestyle

00:21:23.920 --> 00:21:26.800
and the fad that says
this is the best…

00:21:26.800 --> 00:21:28.960
So today they will buy furniture,
and then throw it away…

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:34.240
It's a style. Lifestyle, they say…

00:21:34.240 --> 00:21:37.360
Choices you say?
Choices… So many choices!

00:21:37.360 --> 00:21:41.680
And these choices I have discussed —
that they have choices

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:42.760
which have no meaning…

00:21:42.760 --> 00:21:45.520
They go on changing for what?
I mean…

00:21:45.520 --> 00:21:47.920
It is just to show off
that you have money.

00:21:47.920 --> 00:21:55.040
So the reaction of polarity acts…

00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:58.480
Then another extreme is —
too much running after money,

00:21:58.480 --> 00:22:01.760
we neglect our children,
we neglect the family,

00:22:01.760 --> 00:22:04.560
and all these problems
start coming up.

00:22:04.560 --> 00:22:07.440
And if the children are neglected
they can go to any extreme…

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:09.440
As you have seen,
they get to violence,

00:22:09.440 --> 00:22:11.520
they get to all kinds of things…

00:22:11.520 --> 00:22:15.440
But children are very important
because they are future citizens…

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:19.200
And their preservation
is extremely important,

00:22:19.200 --> 00:22:22.000
so I have also started
an NGO in India

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:25.840
where we are looking after
the children of destitute women.

00:22:25.840 --> 00:22:27.920
We are also having
a school for them…

00:22:27.920 --> 00:22:32.480
Already we have a school
for foreign children,

00:22:32.480 --> 00:22:34.960
because they want to send
their children to India

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:36.000
to be educated.

00:22:36.000 --> 00:22:39.280
And they have turned out to be
such beautiful children,

00:22:39.280 --> 00:22:42.960
such good children,
very smart, very intelligent…

00:22:42.960 --> 00:22:47.600
Always from India, the boys and girls
from our schools top the list…

00:22:48.720 --> 00:22:51.760
Wonderful! I think it's
very important…

00:22:51.760 --> 00:22:55.200
Really, Hitler had started
with the youth

00:22:55.200 --> 00:22:59.120
to get control of Germany
because they were so impressionable,

00:22:59.120 --> 00:23:03.360
so it's important to teach them
the right values!

00:23:03.360 --> 00:23:06.080
Right values are taught also
by parents…

00:23:06.080 --> 00:23:08.640
You see, if the parents are
all the time fighting

00:23:08.640 --> 00:23:12.160
and there is no peace,
then children start their own ways

00:23:12.160 --> 00:23:14.240
and go to another side.

00:23:14.240 --> 00:23:16.560
But I can't understand
why can't we have

00:23:16.560 --> 00:23:18.080
beautiful families?

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:22.400
And why can't we have people
who respect each other

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:26.560
and have children
who can respect them also?

00:23:26.560 --> 00:23:28.400
Respect begets respect…

00:23:28.400 --> 00:23:30.800
In the family, if the husband
is saying all kinds of things

00:23:30.800 --> 00:23:32.080
to his wife,
and the wife is saying

00:23:32.080 --> 00:23:35.280
all kinds of things…
Children become…

00:23:37.040 --> 00:23:40.160
It is very subtle…
We don't realize

00:23:40.160 --> 00:23:41.680
how harmful it could be…

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:44.320
But if you realize it,
you will try to avoid this…

00:23:44.320 --> 00:23:49.920
No need to have
this kind of atmosphere.

00:23:49.920 --> 00:23:53.760
Then another problem is that
this so-called affluence

00:23:53.760 --> 00:23:56.800
makes people go crazy sometimes.

00:23:56.800 --> 00:24:00.480
They really go crazy,
because with affluence

00:24:00.480 --> 00:24:07.520
they take to horrible things
like drugs, alcoholism,

00:24:07.520 --> 00:24:10.400
all kinds of things,
and then they go mad.

00:24:10.400 --> 00:24:14.160
I have also started an NGO
for drug addicts

00:24:14.160 --> 00:24:17.600
in a place called Kanhajohri
in North India…

00:24:17.600 --> 00:24:20.480
I am thinking of starting
a big place

00:24:20.480 --> 00:24:22.720
for people who are drug addicts…

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:25.520
And you can cure the drug addiction
overnight…

00:24:26.880 --> 00:24:29.600
It's a fact.
This happens…

00:24:29.600 --> 00:24:34.160
And you don't have to pay for it
because it is your own power…

00:24:34.160 --> 00:24:37.760
So there is a place
I am trying to get

00:24:37.760 --> 00:24:39.840
where we can accommodate people.

00:24:39.840 --> 00:24:43.680
And I talked to the people there,
they said our government

00:24:43.680 --> 00:24:46.320
will be happy,
but the people will be against it…

00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:47.760
I said for what?

00:24:47.760 --> 00:24:52.160
Because all kinds of permissions
you have to have.

00:24:52.160 --> 00:24:53.760
But I said why?

00:24:53.760 --> 00:24:55.440
So they said people
will go amok

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:58.080
and will try to destroy
the houses and all that.

00:24:58.080 --> 00:25:01.440
I said, Kanhajohri
is such a cut-off place.

00:25:01.440 --> 00:25:04.080
Even to walk off there
is difficult,

00:25:04.080 --> 00:25:06.000
you can't even have
a horse ride.

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:08.800
So who is going to come out
of it to trouble the public?

00:25:08.800 --> 00:25:10.560
It's a very far-fetched place…

00:25:10.560 --> 00:25:12.480
So nothing like that
will happen.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:16.400
But unnecessarily,
you create a problem —

00:25:16.400 --> 00:25:19.600
everything that goes well,
what can be done?

00:25:19.600 --> 00:25:22.560
Your children would be
saved entirely.

00:25:22.560 --> 00:25:28.000
Absolutely, we have so many —
first in England, drug addicts —

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:30.640
When they came,
they saw just lights,

00:25:30.640 --> 00:25:31.680
this and that…

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:33.520
Today they are very good
Sahaja Yogis.

00:25:33.520 --> 00:25:37.200
They are doing very good work,
they are well educated…

00:25:37.840 --> 00:25:42.000
It's a very different area
you entered.

00:25:42.000 --> 00:25:50.000
You take drugs to avoid problems,
here the problems disappear.

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:52.080
Shri Mataji!
Sahaja Yoga is the hope

00:25:52.080 --> 00:25:52.800
for the world…

00:25:52.800 --> 00:25:54.480
Of course, it is, no doubt…

00:25:54.480 --> 00:26:03.120
But unfortunately in America,
it's not so popular…

00:26:03.120 --> 00:26:05.520
I had a lot of people who come
and ask how much it costs.

00:26:07.920 --> 00:26:11.440
Because you don't take money,
that's why they are not interested…

00:26:11.440 --> 00:26:14.320
I mean I can't take money,
whether you are interested or not…

00:26:14.320 --> 00:26:18.320
But isn't it true that even 1%
of the population,

00:26:18.320 --> 00:26:20.800
if changed,
would have such a ripple effect

00:26:20.800 --> 00:26:22.000
on the world?

00:26:22.000 --> 00:26:26.640
Yes, but difficult it is
that they have certain concepts

00:26:27.280 --> 00:26:28.080
about things,

00:26:28.080 --> 00:26:32.320
and all people who are very clever
and cunning —

00:26:32.320 --> 00:26:35.200
more so than me —
come and exploit them,

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:39.360
and they like it…
They like exploitation…

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:42.640
We have so much more to talk about!
I thank you so much.

00:26:42.640 --> 00:26:45.040
I know you get up very early
to come here…

00:26:45.040 --> 00:26:46.320
And it's so wonderful…

00:26:46.320 --> 00:26:48.640
No, I get up early always!

00:26:48.640 --> 00:26:49.793
Thank you!

00:26:49.793 --> 00:26:49.821
Nice to come here!
Thank you!

00:26:49.821 --> 00:26:50.321
That's my pleasure!
Thank you!

00:26:52.480 --> 00:26:53.360
May God bless you!

00:26:53.360 --> 00:26:55.840
This is Audrey Hope,
in Reel Woman,

00:26:55.840 --> 00:26:58.240
dedicated to life
and perspectives

00:26:58.240 --> 00:27:00.320
that can transform our world.

00:27:00.320 --> 00:27:12.080
Thank you so much
for joining us!

